,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T12:08:41.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ebe9cc5375506cba0f7c6feffac241d39f6fe5eb","tid":2208530,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f0935eb3851f1f811c1d6b038b7bcd4936ae3194","tid":2208530,"uid":139294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T12:08:41.000Z","msg":"Push"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T12:12:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DtXmrM9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDtXmrM9.jpg&h=9132d44e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n妳含冤而逝一年，尚未得雪，我們從未放棄找尋真相，但暫時只得到「死因存疑」的法庭裁決。<br />\n<br />\n數月前一段手足上傳的片段中，妳稚嫩而堅定的聲音再次響起。我們心酸、潸然落淚，卻無法挽回悲劇。<br />\n<br />\n隨著妳離去，香港亦步向死亡。惟我們相信，曙光不曾熄滅，就如我們對妳的思念，未曾停息。願他朝再會時，香港已浴火重生，冤情昭雪。<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n🔈民間記者會現有官方帳號：<br />\n<br />\nOfficial webpage: <a href=\"http://www.citizenspc.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.citizenspc.org&d=QA0Qo2zDcB%2FuI%2B3HtJ%2FdCpbpPLVkgxcsq72qYZiHPFQ%3D&h=0557ac7b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.citizenspc.org</a><br />\nTG channel: <a href=\"http://t.me/citizenspresscon\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fcitizenspresscon&d=QA0Qo2zDcB%2FuI%2B3HtJ%2FdCpbpPLVkgxcsq72qYZiHPFQ%3D&h=897c6ebf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/citizenspresscon</a><br />\nFB: <a href=\"http://fb.me/hkercpc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffb.me%2Fhkercpc&d=QA0Qo2zDcB%2FuI%2B3HtJ%2FdCpbpPLVkgxcsq72qYZiHPFQ%3D&h=48042251\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">fb.me/hkercpc</a><br />\nIG: <a href=\"http://www.instagram.com/citizenspresscon\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fcitizenspresscon&d=QA0Qo2zDcB%2FuI%2B3HtJ%2FdCpbpPLVkgxcsq72qYZiHPFQ%3D&h=032f7cec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.instagram.com/citizenspresscon</a><br />\nYouTube: <a href=\"https://bi